Actually, the way to paint plastic parts is to get a paint formulated for
plastic. A company called SEM makes such paint. Before you paint the part,
you have to use an adhesion promoter also made by SEM. Contact your local
auto body paint and supply store to get the product.

Steve Bradley
Bradley Auto Body


